---
layout: base.njk
title: Characters & NPCs
breadcrumb: "NPCs"
---

<p><em>Every face has a story. Every name, a history. These are the people who shaped — or were shaped by — your journey.</em></p>

<div class="ornament">· · ·</div>

<div class="card-grid">
{% for npc in collections.npcs %}
  <a class="card" href="{{ npc.url }}">
    <h3>{{ npc.data.title }}</h3>
    {% if npc.data.role %}<p>{{ npc.data.role }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if npc.data.status %}
    <span class="card-tag">{{ npc.data.status }}</span>
    {% endif %}
  </a>
{% else %}
  <p><em>No NPCs recorded yet.</em></p>
{% endfor %}
</div>
